{"title":"Abbey Bike Tools adds Socket Crombie for Campagnolo cassette lockrings","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/03/18/abbey-bike-tools-adds-socket-crombie-for-campagnolo-cassette-lockrings/","date":1616092701000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>The Abbey Crombie tool is one of the best cassette tools made. It’s what I personally reach for almost every time I’m installing or removing a cassette. But what about those times when that lockring is&nbsp;<em>really</em> tight. Like, gorilla-hanging-off-the-end-of-a-cheater-bar tight? For those instances, you might need a little more leverage. Fortunately, there’s the Socket Crombie tool.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/18142335/Socket-Crombie-cassette-lockring-tool-for-Campagnolo-cassettes-2.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/18142335/Socket-Crombie-cassette-lockring-tool-for-Campagnolo-cassettes-2.jpg\" alt=\"Abbey Bike Tools Socket Crombie \" width=\"1024\" height=\"760\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb8 src ng ngcb8 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/18142335/Socket-Crombie-cassette-lockring-tool-for-Campagnolo-cassettes-2.jpg\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/18142335/Socket-Crombie-cassette-lockring-tool-for-Campagnolo-cassettes-2.jpg 1024w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/18142335/Socket-Crombie-cassette-lockring-tool-for-Campagnolo-cassettes-2-297x220.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/03/18142335/Socket-Crombie-cassette-lockring-tool-for-Campagnolo-cassettes-2-800x594.jpg 800